cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper proposes an algorithm for signal reconstruction from compressed measurements with image priors captured by a generative model. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of compressive sensing also suggests that the paper may belong to the information theory (cs.IT) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Finally, the use of structured latent variables suggests that the paper may also belong to the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
